    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that strikes an optimal balance between performance and value. This unit has been maintained to a high standard, ensuring mechanical reliability and a refined driving experience. Featuring a clean interior and a well-preserved exterior, it represents a sophisticated choice for the discerning driver who prioritizes engineering integrity. Fully inspected and prepared for immediate acquisition.",
