    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been truly well-loved? This beauty is ready for its next adventure! It\u2019s in great shape, runs like a dream, and has plenty of life left in it. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, so it\u2019s perfect if you want a solid, dependable car without that scary brand-new price tag. It\u2019s super clean and drives so smoothly\u2014you\u2019re going to love it! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a quintessential driver's machine, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a documented rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings. The variable M-differential provides exceptional traction out of corners, while the Getrag 6-speed manual offers precise engagement. Maintenance is up to date, including a recent VANOS service and valve adjustment, ensuring the valvetrain is within factory tolerances. While showing minor patina consistent with its age, this example delivers the raw, analog feedback that defines the M-division's golden era.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Runs well. Clean interior. Title in hand.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
